@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_LOGIN

### Create claim (itemId = UUID of an approved lost or found item)
POST {{baseUrl}}/claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
  "message": "This is mine — I can describe distinguishing marks."
}

### List all claims (optional ?status=PENDING|APPROVED|REJECTED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/claims?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### My claims
GET {{baseUrl}}/claims/my-claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Note: ClaimsController has no PATCH /claims/:id.
### Admins approve/reject in admin.http (PUT /admin/claims/:id/approve|reject).
